The bead is done. Here's what was implemented:

**`internal/tui/settings_widget.go`** (new file):
- `settingsWidget` with 4 tabs: General / Filters / Sorting / Theme
- **General**: toggle for `IncludeReviewerMRs`
- **Filters**: reuses `filterStatusWidget` + `filterSelectWidget` with boundary-crossing up/down for section navigation (since tab is reserved for tab switching)
- **Sorting**: radio buttons for sort field (repo·id/author/age) and direction (↑/↓)
- **Theme**: two-pane layout matching the existing theme picker (theme list + mode)
- `SettingsAppliedMsg` emitted live on every change; `SettingsClosedMsg` on close
- `BuildAuthorsReviewers()` helper to extract unique authors/reviewers from MR list

**`internal/tui/model.go`** changes:
- `showSettings`/`settings` fields added
- `,` key opens settings via `openSettings()`  
- `handleSettingsApplied()` applies all live changes (filter, sort, theme, includeReviewerMRs)
- `handleMembersLoaded()` extracted from inline to keep `Update()` cyclomatic complexity at ≤ 30
- Settings overlay rendered in `renderContent`, styles propagated in `applyTheme`
